race.comment: HIGHWAY PRINCESS (4) clocked a sharp 30.51 winning over 550m at Q Lakeside last start in a Grade 5. Has the ability and looks hard to top. ROM BARO (8) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (35.42) last time in a Restricted WIN at this track. Key runner on best form. TOTE DEOR (2) doesn't have the best strike-rate but recent form is sound. Has been in the money the last three starts, the latest when second (35.10) at this track. Winning chance. SHARRI (1) must be included in calculations.
